### initiating project

mkdir server
cd server
npm i -g nodemon
npm i express body-parser bcrypt cors dotenv gridfs-stream multer multer-gridfs-storage helmet morgan jsonwebtoken mongoose
npm install multer@1.4.4 //multer dependency issue with gridfs-storage

npm init -y

